HEADWORD: Encyclopædia
<hw>En*cy`clo*p⟦ae⟧"di*a</hw> }</mhw>
<pr>(?)</pr>, <pos>n.</pos> <ety>[NL., fr. Gr. <?/, for <?/ <?/,
instruction in the circle of arts and sciences: cf. F.
<ets>encyclop⟦eacute⟧die</ets>. See <er>Cyclopedia</er>, and
